  "title": "深度｜暗壳 AI Agent2.0：破局人居行业，链接“设计与交易”的一站式创作生态平台",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247514589&idx=1&sn=30cb409a7ba93934720dfa4b0766efc4",
  "date": "2026-03-16 11:21:00",
