  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.49537037037037035\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/xJ0xcBAKz2ADYPQ0OE4hFs03fbgUJ1NuicEpcCXu6K1icWuesoESDWhVwBaREGyBjiatuEXKJmT9EUxhOvv4VFRrGYI13qSExahLU8rqnkbJSk/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"266\" data-imgfileid=\"100029451\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7bf568b6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FxJ0xcBAKz2ADYPQ0OE4hFs03fbgUJ1NuicEpcCXu6K1icWuesoESDWhVwBaREGyBjiatuEXKJmT9EUxhOvv4VFRrGYI13qSExahLU8rqnkbJSk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">暗壳AI Agent2.0</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">导语</span></font></b></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">当</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI的生成能力逐渐成为标配时，设计AI的竞争核心已不再是谁更会出图，而是谁能真正接管设计师从创意沟通到商业落地的完整工作流，将设计、协同与产业生态整合成一个无缝的系统。这预示着一场范式转移，而最近发布的暗壳AI Agent2.0，或将成为万亿人居产业的生态破局者。</span></font></p>\n  <h2 align=\"center\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 16px 16px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">01 空间设计AI：不应止于设计工具，更需要构建</span></span></span></font></b><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">生态</span></span></span></font></b></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">空间设计远非纯粹的美学创作，其本质是一个极其复杂的商业流程。它始于模糊的客户沟通，贯穿概念构思、方案迭代、预算控制、供应链协调，最终才抵达物理世界的落地施工</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\">。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__10\">这是一个融合了沟通学、项目管理、供应链配套和美学判断的系统工程</span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__11\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">但过去几年的AI设计工具，绝大多数停留在单一功能层面。用户在短暂试用后，发现这些工具难以融入自己既有的工作流，最终只是将其当作一个偶尔使用的“灵感插件\"，而非不可或缺的生产力系统。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__12\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">行业真正的痛点，并非创意生成的效率，而是隐藏在整个项目周期中，那漫长、琐碎且昂贵的沟通与修改成本。客户一句</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“想要一点松弛感”，背后是设计师数轮方案的揣摩、修改和确认。这个过程的成本，远比单纯出图高昂得多。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__13\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">因此，空间设计</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI的下一阶段，必然要从比拼生成效果的能力展示，转向比拼任务组织能力的工作流系统。答案，正指向一种新的产品形态——垂直于特定行业的AI Agent。它不再是单一工具，而是一个能理解行业任务、主动推进流程、并整合产业资源的生态枢纽。它能接住“松弛感”这样的模糊需求，将其拆解为一系列任务，并调度不同能力模块去完成。以暗壳AI Agent2.0为代表的AI产品，它们试图从根本上改变游戏规则——不再是辅助设计师的工具，而是成为组织整个工作流的生态系统。</span></font></p>\n  <h2 align=\"center\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 16px 16px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__14\"><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__15\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">02 暗壳AI Agent 2.0：以系统架构，重构泛家居智能设计全链路</span></span></span></font></b></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__17\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">暗壳的产品逻辑，正是对空间设计领域全链路工作流的系统性思路的一次具体实践。它将自己的核心定位明确为</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“人人可用的空间智能设计Agent”。为了实现这一目标，它构建了“AI Agent + 协同自由画布 + 专业Skills技能库 + 行业生态库 + 数字资产管理”的创新架构。这个创新架构，旨在解决AI在目前空间设计、家居产品设计、家居营销设计、家居导购、家居品牌出海等工作流中的多个关键难题，如：用户意图理解模糊、多软件跳转且协同困难、专业门槛高影响成果效果、产业供需匹配失衡和数字资产运营低效等。</span></font></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__18\"><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">1.&nbsp;</span></font></b><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">意图理解</span></font></b><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">：最懂设计的行业垂类</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Agent</span></font></b></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__19\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">工作流的起点是需求。暗壳</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI Agent首先要解决的，就是将用户模糊、情绪化的语言，翻译成可执行的设计指令。其内置的AI智能体如同一位资深设计顾问。当用户输入“我想要一个有呼吸感的侘寂风客厅”，它不会立刻出图，而是通过智能推理反问：“您希望的‘呼吸感’是侧重于大面积留白，还是通过材质的通透性来实现？”</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__20\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这种基于上下文感知的对话，能逐步厘清用户真实需求，有效避免因表达偏差导致的生图效果不理想。同时，它支持图文多模态输入，能深度解析参考图，甚至自动优化提示词，让设计落地更精准。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.7311111111111112\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"900\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/xJ0xcBAKz2AhWA3ZSd5XsQiaYLY583JYQ1GFKMy5MFGY15XqsnyhYynERasJr7dqlGSicGzkXgsKgn68Uibphd9SyCeUrb8t9tT2L1w6cBm7m0/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"426\" data-imgfileid=\"100029447\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea434d4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxJ0xcBAKz2AhWA3ZSd5XsQiaYLY583JYQ1GFKMy5MFGY15XqsnyhYynERasJr7dqlGSicGzkXgsKgn68Uibphd9SyCeUrb8t9tT2L1w6cBm7m0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">暗</span></span><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">壳AI Agent2.0，</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">电脑端、手机端皆可使用</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-se