t:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__50\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">暗壳</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI的护城河，首先来自对行业知识的深度掌握。相较于通用AI，上万名专业设计师的持续调优，使其更懂泛家居行业的设计标准与落地痛点。当底层模型能力逐渐拉齐，对垂直工作流颗粒度的精准把控，正成为应用层真正的壁垒。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__51\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在行业深度理解之上，还有其自研技术体系支撑。暗壳</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI Agent2.0基于MoE（混合专家模型）架构，构建了多智能体协作体系，让不同AI像人类专家团队一样协同工作。除此之外，还有基于百万级行业私有数据训练</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">自研的多模态空间美学大模型、空间风格模型、控制生成模型等多个垂类模型。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__52\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">正是这套为行业深度定制的体系架构，支撑起一个连接设计师、供应链与终端客户的复杂产业生态。它的护城河不再是单纯的模型能力，而是融合了行业</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">knowhow、业务流程以及商业链路的产业生态系统，这才是难以复制的核心优势。</span></font></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 16px 16px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__53\"><b><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"js_darkmode__54\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">结论</span></span></span></font></b></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__56\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">讨论暗壳</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI Agent2.0的意义，已不局限于它是否是一个更好的设计工具。它更重要的价值，在于揭示了AI应用的一种进化方向：从提供SaaS工具，到构建一个连接设计师、品牌方与终端消费者的产业生态平台。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__57\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">最终，暗壳</span></font><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI Agent2.0提出的问题是，当AI能够组织和连接产业时，我们购买的究竟是一个软件，还是一个通往新商业生态的入口？这或许才是AI应用竞争的真正终局。</span></font></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "暗壳 AI Agent 2.0 通过整合 AI 智能体、协同画布与行业供应链，构建了从设计创意到商业落地的全链路闭环，重塑泛家居行业工作流。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "暗壳 AI Agent 2.0 通过整合 AI 智能体、协同画布与行业供应链，构建了从设计创意到商业落地的全链路闭环，重塑泛家居行业工作流。",
  "summary": "本文深入剖析了暗壳（Anke）AI Agent 2.0 的产品逻辑与行业价值。文章指出，空间设计 AI 的竞争已从单纯的“生图”转向“工作流接管”。暗壳 2.0 通过“AI Agent + 协同自由画布 + 专业技能库 + 行业生态库”的创新架构，解决了需求理解模糊、工具割裂、专业门槛高及供需匹配失衡等痛点。其核心优势在于基于 MoE 架构的多智能体协作，以及与百家家居品牌联动的生态库，实现了“以设计链接交易”的商业闭环，标志着 AI 应用从 SaaS 工具向产业生态平台的进化。",
